sources.title: 1959 - Insect Woman - Strong men forced to satisfy a passion no human knows 4K
sources.description:
Cosmetics mogul Janice Starlin (Susan Cabot) panics when sales drop because she's aging. She funds rogue scientist Dr. Zinthrop (Michael Mark), who's discovered anti-aging enzymes in wasp venom. After impatiently injecting extra doses, Janice sheds 20 years... but gets a monstrous side effect: she transforms into a winged terror! With Zinthrop missing after an accident, Janice's secret spirals into a stinging nightmare.

metadata.Plot: A schoolgirl goes from braids to bouffant when her mother makes her a bar hostess/prostitute. She cures impotence for Professor Lee and becomes his concubine. His entrepreneurial wife is initially shocked but soon accepts the arrangement and even gives the girl and allowance.
metadata.Actors: Won Namkung, Youn Yuh-jung, Gye-hyeon Jeon
